The '''Birtraub Brothers Storage and Reclamation Center''' was an immense storage center near [[Crovna]]'s main [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]]. A mass of gray buildings, it served forty ships at any given time. It was a front for the criminal enterprises of the [[Birtraub Brothers]].
The outlet on Crovna housed some of the [[BloodScar]] pirate gang's stolen items in warehouse 13 around [[0 ABY/Legends|0.5 ABY]].

